  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Released 10/03/17 2:08 CT (19:08 UTC)</p><h2 id=\"id-1.13.6-TicketNotesinNotifications\">Ticket Notes in Notifications</h2><p>A new shortcode\u00a0is available for automated notifications to include customer facing (printable) notes in ticket notifications.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.13.6-CustomFormOrder\">Custom Form Order</h2><p>The sort order of custom forms on tickets now sorts based on the\u00a0order number\u00a0from\u00a0your custom form settings.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.13.6-CashReconciliationPrint-pagebreaks\">Cash Reconciliation Print - page breaks</h2><p>The forced page break\u00a0before the &quot;notes&quot; section has been removed.\u00a0This\u00a0will reduce the number of pages printed.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.13.6-Timesheetswithduplicatestaffnames\">Timesheets with duplicate staff names</h2><p>We fixed an issue with grouping\u00a0and displaying results where\u00a0two staff have the exact\u00a0same first and last name.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.13.6-OnboardingVideos\">Onboarding Videos</h2><p>We added direct access to the onboarding videos from the dashboard.</p>",
